file.name: positive5.yaml
file.content:
openapi: 3.0.0
info:
  title: Simple API Overview
  version: 1.0.0
paths:
  "/":
    get:
      operationId: listVersionsv2
      summary: List API versions
      responses:
        '200':
          description: Success
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                "$ref": "#/components/schemas/MyObject"
              examples:
                objectExample:
                  "$ref": "#/components/examples/objectExample"
components:
  schemas:
    MyObject:
      type: object
      required:
      - id
      properties:
        id:
          type: integer
          minLength: 1
        name:
          type: string
          minLength: 3
        phones:
          type: array
          items:
            type: string
            pattern: "\\(\\d{3}\\) ?\\d{3}-\\d{4}"
          minItems: 1
  examples:
    objectExample:
      value:
        id: '1'
        name: new object
      summary: A sample object
